        "url": "https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/7/"
      },
      "text": "Lanza grandes pedruscos. Puede amedrentar al objetivo.",
      "version_group": {
        "name": "sword-shield",
        "url": "https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/20/"
      }
    },
    {
      "language": {
        "name": "it",
        "url": "https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/8/"
      },
      "text": "I nemici vengono colpiti con violenza da grandi\nmassi che possono anche farli tentennare.",
      "version_group": {
        "name": "sword-shield",
        "url": "https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/20/"
      }
    },
    {
      "language": {
        "name": "en",
        "url": "https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/9/"
      },
      "text": "Large boulders are hurled at opposing Pokémon to\ninflict damage. This may also make the opposing\nPokémon flinch.",
      "version_group": {
        "name": "sword-shield",
        "url": "https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/20/"
      }
    },
    {
      "language": {
        "name": "ja",
        "url": "https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/11/"
      },
      "text": "大きな　岩を\n激しく　ぶつけて　攻撃する。\n相手を　ひるませることが　ある。",
      "version_group": {
        "name": "sword-shield",
        "url": "https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/20/"
      }
    },
    {
      "language": {
        "name": "zh-hans",
        "url": "https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/12/"
      },
      "text": "将大岩石\n猛烈地撞向对手进行攻击。\n有时会使对手畏缩。",
      "version_group": {
        "name": "sword-shield",
        "url": "https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/20/"
      }
